t: Guinness Agrees to Buy All-Brand Importers | AP News
s: January 30, 1990 - NEW YORK (AP) _ Guinness Import Co. said Tuesday it has agreed to acquire All Brand Importers Inc. and the rights to distribute several of its brands, including Moosehead Premium Canadian Lager and Dos Equis, for $21 million.
